OL,6,FA detective who had "wholly
OL,7,Finappropriate" sexual relationships
OL,8,Fwith multiple women he met while on
OL,9,Fduty with the police would have been
OL,10,Ffired had he not already retired.
OL,12,FEx-detective constable Simon Jones was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of gross misconduct and
OL,14,Fbreaching standards of police
OL,15,Fprofessional behaviour at a hearing in
OL,16,FPortishead on 3 September.
OL,18,FHe had been arrested in 2021 over the
OL,19,Fallegations.
