OL,6,FIn one case, Jones was investigating
OL,7,Fan assault on a teenage child. Due to
OL,8,Fthe victim's age, the boy's mother was
OL,9,Fthe point of contact for Jones to
OL,10,Fupdate.
OL,12,FThe investigation into Jones' conduct
OL,13,Ffound he sent multiple flirtatious
OL,14,Fmessages to the boy's mother during
OL,15,Fthe investigation of the criminal
OL,16,Fcase, leading to a relationship that
OL,17,Flasted several years.
