OL,8,Fmeaning there was no policing purpose
OL,9,Ffor doing so.
OL,11,FIn late 2019, Jones was assigned to
OL,12,Finvestigate an allegation of crime
OL,13,Finvolving a female victim.
OL,15,FIt was alleged their relationship
OL,16,Fcrossed from professional to personal
OL,17,Fwithin a couple of months.
