OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police then received
OL,7,Fan anonymous report in August 2020
OL,8,Fthat then-DC Jones was in a
OL,9,Frelationship with a 'victim of crime'.
OL,11,FThis led to his work mobile phone
OL,12,Fbilling being reviewed and it was
OL,13,Ffound he had a large amount of contact
OL,14,Fwith the woman, beyond the criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation concluding.
OL,17,FThree months later in November, the
OL,18,Fforce discovered the previous
OL,19,Frelationship Jones had been involved
OL,20,Fin with the mother from 2017.
