OL,6,FThis led to the force's counter-
OL,7,Fcorruption unit carrying out criminal
OL,8,Fand misconduct investigations, under
OL,9,Fthe direction of the IOPC.
OL,11,FOfficers examined Jones' devices
OL,12,Fduring the investigation, which
OL,13,Frevealed that his devices had been
OL,14,Flocated at the address of one of the
OL,15,Fwomen overnight and at hotels she had
OL,16,Fstayed at on many occasions.
OL,18,FThose investigating him also found
OL,19,Fthat Jones advised one of the women to
OL,20,Fbuy a 'burner type' phone to help
OL,21,Fconceal their relationship.
