OL,6,FDuring an ethical interview with Avon
OL,7,Fand Somerset police in 2020 about one
OL,8,Frelationship, Jones described it as
OL,9,F"platonic" and despite being told to
OL,10,Fend it, carried on an intimate
OL,11,Frelationship.
OL,13,FThe police disciplinary panel was
OL,14,Foverseen by a legally qualified chair
OL,15,Fand decided Jones was guilty of gross
OL,16,Fmisconduct. It also found he had
OL,17,Fbreached standards of police
OL,18,Fprofessional behaviour in respect of
OL,19,Fhonesty and integrity; authority,
OL,20,Frespect and courtesy; and
OL,21,Fdiscreditable conduct.
