OL,9,Fwas doing was wrong'
OL,11,FFollowing the investigation, which saw
OL,12,FJones arrested in 2021, a file was
OL,13,Fsent to the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,14,Fwho decided not to bring any criminal
OL,15,Fcharges.
OL,17,FBut the former detective was subjected
OL,18,Fto the misconduct hearing, which found
OL,19,Fhim guilty.
