OL,7,Fthe Professional Standards Department
OL,8,Fat Avon and Somerset Police, said:
OL,9,F"There is no place in policing, or any
OL,10,Flaw enforcement agency, for anyone who
OL,11,Fbehaves in the way Simon Jones did.
