OL,6,F"He was deliberately dishonest when
OL,7,Fchallenged and sought to cover his
OL,8,Ftracks by several means, when he
OL,9,Ffeared the truth would be revealed.
OL,11,F"We are grateful to those people who
OL,12,Fsupplied information because it
OL,13,Fenabled us to not only take misconduct
OL,14,Faction against him for these matters,
OL,15,Fbut also revealed abhorrent messages
OL,16,Fhe sent about colleagues.
OL,18,F"We hope this outcome reassures the
OL,19,Fpublic we will take positive action to
OL,20,Fremove any officer who behaves in such
OL,21,Fan inappropriate manner."
